{"tid":1904331,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［Linear]何柏良：靠政府會好大鑊，香港人時代抗疫， 做得好！","createTime":"2020-02-29T14:21:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T14:26:53.000Z","uid":48083,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"125e979c07516a8c0f26d21b56e3ad06fd214553","tid":1904331,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T14:21:34.000Z","msg":"香港人時代抗疫, 做得好！<br />\n<br />\n從 1 月 31 日起，香港人自發疫境自強，落實四大措施：全民戴口罩、 勤洗手、 嚴防厠、堅持社交距離。跟住 &hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0nJ31gC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0nJ31gC.jpg&h=7980946b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1. 流感被迫提早收工（冬季流感高峰期：今年 34 days vs 98.7 days +/- 26 days for the past 7 years）<br />\n<br />\n2. 所有呼吸道病毒陽性檢測結果👇，全線急降，其中流感 flu，副流感 paraflu，呼吸道融合病毒 RSV，&ldquo;斷崖式&rdquo;下降 &hellip; 基本歸零，腺病毒 adenovirus、鼻病毒 rhinovirus、 人類偏肺病毒，都一樣。按數據，呢點香港人做得好過好過 2003 年！<br />\n<br />\n3. 不過，疫情仲係好嚴峻，絕對不能放鬆；<br />\n<br />\n4. 新沙士疫情穩定有幾個條件：a) 所有類別新沙土要連續 14 天歸零，先至算穩定；b) 內地所有省市同樣連續 14 天歸零；c) 大中華地區意外，其他國家亦以相同標準穩定。<br />\n<br />\n#感謝香港人<br />\n#新沙士<br />\n#疫境自強<br />\n#靠政府會好大鑊<br />\n#衛生防護中心病毒化驗檢測數據<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB-%E5%81%9A%E5%BE%97%E5%A5%BD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2596%25AB-%25E5%2581%259A%25E5%25BE%2597%25E5%25A5%25BD%2F&d=EEQ1dbVkwObjLGYhXKOOXGsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=4f2062c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2596%25AB-%25E5%2581%259A%25E5%25BE%2597%25E5%25A5%25BD%2F&h=cd0890f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB-%E5%81%9A%E5%BE%97%E5%A5%BD/</a>"},{"pi